Package be.belgium.eid.objects

Interface Summary
SmartCardReadable This interface can be used by the implementing class to define an object that can be read from a smart card.
 

Class Summary
IDAddress The IDAddress class represents the address of the holder of the current beID card.
IDData The IDData class represents the ID data of a certain beID card.
IDPhoto The IDPhoto class contains the photo of the holder of the current beID card.
IDPIN The IDPIN class contains the information of a PIN, there are 1 or more on the beID card.
IDTokenInfo The IDTokenInfo class contains the token information of the smart card.
IDVersion The IDPIN class contains the version information of the smart card.
 

Enum Summary
PINType This enumeration contains the different kinds of PIN types that can occur.
PINUsageCode This enumeration contains the different kinds of usages for which the PIN is used (for authentication or for signing).
